sequenceDiagram
	autonumber
	participant S as Scheduler
	participant W as Analytics Worker
	participant M as MongoDB
	participant R as Redis
	participant API as Express API
	participant C as Client SPA

	S->>W: Hourly trigger per region
	W->>M: aggregate order volume 24h
	W->>M: aggregate price velocity 7d
	W->>W: compute composite score
	W->>R: ZADD kmb:trending:crops:{region} score crop
	W->>R: EXPIRE kmb:trending:crops:{region} 3600
	C->>API: GET /v1/analytics/trending?region=IN-HR
	API->>R: ZREVRANGE kmb:trending:crops:IN-HR 0 9 WITHSCORES
	R-->>API: top crops + scores
	API-->>C: 200 application/json

